Name: uDom-DelegatedRight-ManageAD
Description: Members are granted Full Control over \uDom\* OUs and modify rights to the Managed Service Accounts container.

Name: uDom-DelegatedRight-ManageAD-ENG
Description: Members are delegated rights equivalent to Domain Admins in uDom.

Name: uDom-DelegatedRight-ManagePKI
Description: Members can publish and manage PKI in Active Directory in uDom.

Name: uDom-DelegatedRight-ManageGroups
Description: Members can manage AD group memberships in uDom.

Name: uDom-DelegatedRight-ManageSVRCompObjs
Description: Members can join servers to the uDom domain.

Name: uDom-DelegatedRight-ManageUsers
Description: Members can manage AD users in uDom.

Name: uDom-DelegatedRight-ManageWKSCompObjs
Description: Members can join workstations to the uDom domain.

Name: uDom-Admins-AD-ENG
Description: Members are domain local administrators in uDom.

Name: uDom-Admins-AD-OPS
Description: Members who administer AD, but are NOT Domain Admins, in uDom.

Name: uDom-Admins-BigFix
Description: Members are BigFix administrators in uDom.

Name: uDom-Admins-DNS
Description: Members granted DNS Administrator rights in uDom.

Name: uDom-Admins-PKI
Description: Members are granted 'Local Admin' rights on the PKI servers in uDom.

Name: uDom-SVR-Auditors
Description: Members are granted rights to read security logs on member servers in uDom.

Name: uDom-SVR-Auditors-DCs
Description: Members are granted rights to read security logs on domain controllers in uDom.

Name: uDom-SVR-Local-Admins
Description: Members granted local administrator rights on all member servers in uDom.

Name: uDom-SVR-Local-Admins-DCs
Description: Members granted local administrator rights on domain controllers in uDom.

Name: uDom-SVR-RSA-NoChallenge
Description: Members are not challeged via RSA in uDom.

Name: uDom-WKS-Local-Admins
Description: Members granted local administrator rights on workstations in uDom.

Name: uDom-WKS-RSA-NoChallenge
Description: Members are not challeged via RSA in uDom.
